*libvirt-0.7.6 (03 Feb 2010)

  03 Feb 2010; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> +libvirt-0.7.6.ebuild:
  version bump. fix bug #302443 & bug #293416

  06 Jan 2010; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> libvirt-0.7.5.ebuild:
